2018-04-20
Adapt mpd configuration to new Buildroot Layout. New standard configuration is

  storage ::= local
  neighbour ::= upnp
  input ::= curl, file
  decoder ::= flac, dsdiff, dsf, mad, sndfile
  encoder ::= 
  resampler ::= libsamplerate, soxr
  output ::= alsa

